name: Christopher_Knight_Home_Two_Door_Sideboard
description: Clever routed detailing and two decorative rows of metal knobs, give this two-door piece the look of a vintage fourteen-drawer map cabinet. Soaring tapered legs and a double-bow front are bold yet fitting design choices. The interior is divided into two shelved spaces to maximize storage.
